name: ems-web-app-seat-time
author: Chris Spence (https://educationalmediasolutions.com)
description: This angular.io component starts a session timer that pauses after periods of inactivity or when the containg web browser loses focus.

scripts.publish: git add -A . && git commit -m 'prepublish npm package' && npm version patch && ng build SeatTime && cd dist && npm publish
